title: How Can She Help Her Husband Gain Confidence In The Bedroom?
description:
Her husband lied to her about his sexual history before they go together. He recently shared his confession, and she's not upset. Instead, she wants to help him gain his confidence by spicing things up in the bedroom. Is her plan a good idea or not?
